author: @briandubois-gilbert8182
content: Her good karma, her advocacy/humanitarian support for many who are marginalized in society, her embrace of multiculturalism, of inclusion, tolerance, respect for diversity, for individual choices and freedoms have impacted many for the better—much better than the hate, intolerance, prejudice and religious bigotry that she’s courageously faced throughout her life and career.  For all of this, fate have smiled on her and guided her on her journey in this life.
